    "Html": "\r\n<p>Hi. I have a project that uses the galasoft mvvm light toolkit. I have a problem.</p>\r\n<p>I need to catch changes to a property in my viewmodel from my codebehind. I already did bind in my xaml and that works fine. However I need to do other things from the codebehind when the propery in the viewmodel changes. Im using the observableobject. Could\r\n someone provide an example how to catch those events in the View codebehind plz? I assume its quite simple, however Googling has brought me nowhere :-)</p>\r\n",
    "PostedDate": "2012-02-19T09:38:34.623-08:00",
    "UserRole": null,
    "MarkedAsAnswerDate": null
