    "Id": "780610",
    "ThreadId": "327751",
    "Html": "<p>Thx. I follow you all the way to the eventhandler. Could you show me in example.</p>\r\n<p>If this is my viewModel object</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\">public</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\">string</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">WelcomeTitle\r\n<p>{</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\">get</span></p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p>{</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\">return</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">_welcomeTitle;\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\">set</span></p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p>{</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\">if</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"> (_welcomeTitle == </span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\">value</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">)\r\n<p>{</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\">return</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">;\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p>_welcomeTitle =</p>\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\">value</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">;\r\n<p>RaisePropertyChanged(WelcomeTitlePropertyName);</p>\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; font-size: x-small;\"></span>How do attach that as an eventhandler in my View?</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n</span></p>",
